A mụrụ Nafisa Ali na Kolkata, ada Ahmed Ali, nwoke onye Alakụba Bengali na Philomena Torresan, nwanyị Roman Katọlik nke ihe nketa Anglo-India
Wajid Ali, bụ onye ode akwụkwọ ama ama na Bengali
Nwanne nna ya (nwanne nna) bụ Zaib-un-Nissa Hamidullah, onye odeakụkọ Pakistani na onye na-ahụ maka nwanyị
Nafisa nwekwara ihe jikọrọ ya na onye agha nnwere onwe Bangladesh a ma ama na onye agha Bir Pratik Akhtar Ahmed
